dct_description_sm: This map includes three maps of coastline and coastal land area, primarily in Ocean County, all arranged on one paper. The map also lists bodies of water, some land forms and man-made features like train stations. There are red lines and some scant handwritten notes inscribed on the map. The map has multiple tears.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
The map misspells Metedeconk River as Meteticonk.
